snippet.title: Member of War - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
​Member of War is a multi-player / multi-player co-öp game in which player takes control of military vehicle and fights against players of enemy team using standard or sci-fi weapons, like plasma or laser guns.

Download the game at: https://sweetproductions.itch.io/member-of-war

Every donation is welcome and will be used to fund the project.

Donations can be send to our PayPal adress: info.crimetimeonline@gmail.com
